{"tid":527877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[難民之父]張超雄畀人質疑緊老吹屋崙市定「張超雄日」表揚佢貢獻","createTime":"2018-01-13T06:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T05:37:07.000Z","uid":57035,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b15c71c95dc69a777db713fa01bd4b18ede788c2","tid":527877,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wai.yeung.7/posts/1531462433641867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwai.yeung.7%2Fposts%2F1531462433641867&d=LP8yUVPm7W3rfFmF2OgoJsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=ba99bb0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wai.yeung.7/posts/1531462433641867</a><br />\n找不到張超雄日<br />\n1月4日，我在這裡貼文，題名是「張超雄日」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">張超雄議員在他的網站說，<br />\n「張超雄長期關注貧窮問題，對貧富懸殊、社會保障、殘疾人士需要、家庭暴力等重要社會議題有深入了解。此外，他亦致力推動公民社會發展，捍衛人權和社會公義等價值。在留美期間，張超雄一直爭取當地亞裔人士權益，更獲屋崙（奧克蘭）市政府把9月13日訂為Dr. Fernando Cheung&rsquo;s Day，以紀念他的貢獻。</span></strong><br />\n.................................<br />\n1990年加州大學(柏克萊分校)社會福利博士，定居加州時，於「屋崙華人服務社」擔任總幹事八年。離任時，屋崙市定立九月十三日為張超雄日，以示表揚。」<br />\n屋崙華人服務社是家橋譯社的前身。當日，我打電話到家橋譯社問那裡的人，她說不知道有張超雄日。<br />\n屋崙市政府大樓就在我工作地點旁邊。今天到屋崙市政府大樓的3樓市長辦公室查問。接待員不知道張超雄日的事情，於是找來市長助理。市長助理找了一會，完全沒有任何關於9月13日是張超雄日的記錄。我本來想到二樓的崙市議會查問，市長助理說她找不到任何記錄，市議會也不會找到。她叫我直接到一樓市政府書記處找。若果有張超雄日，市政府一定有決議案。有決議案的話，書記處一定有存檔。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>書記處的負責人找了半小時，找不到張超雄日的相關記錄。我只能拿到書記處的證明書，說沒有記錄。</strong></span><br />\n張超雄的個人資料說屋崙市政府將9月13日定為張超雄日，Dr. Fernando Cheung's Day。但是屋崙市政府沒有相關記錄，張博士，張議員有必要出來澄清，到底這是甚麼一回事。"},{"pid":"6997cabae6c3ef2d5c42b076b560a916b13a0056","tid":527877,"uid":42691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"在美國加州定居期間，為華人爭取權益，加州屋崙市長Elihu Harris定了<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1996年9月13日</span></span>（即離開服務六年的屋倫服務社的那天）為Dr. Fernando Chiu Hung Cheung Day（張超雄日），表彰他對當地社區的貢獻。[4]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會只係1996年既9月13日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae127f3804f880753b1e04f85b4383a157d67ea","tid":527877,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"冇人討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdc513e8f1dbd0c4bdfbcfa530b2b3efdc660e8","tid":527877,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c89c99bb300b17a17ac947cb59265611e57a8a","tid":527877,"uid":121131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/215226_644f87a8c4f9c9badfbde8987f7af2a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F215226_644f87a8c4f9c9badfbde8987f7af2a6.png&h=aef3aaf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20ba48ac0890b44a3aa8bbcdf61683b086d5b69b","tid":527877,"uid":121131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"個post可以沉了"},{"pid":"52870d31e3b26bd42a0f60a175dfae64481d7a7e","tid":527877,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20ba48ac0890b44a3aa8bbcdf61683b086d5b69b","tid":527877,"uid":121131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"個post可以沉了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"市長本人同市政府唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222c631cab0d46e54cb048e4f494e06afb6576b6","tid":527877,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wai.yeung.7/posts/1531623406959103\" data-sr-url=\"https:/